{"tid":801703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美籍華裔癌症研究專家Yu Xue盜商業機密售中國 或被追討195億元賠償","createTime":"2018-09-01T01:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T03:24:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"47c887f6ab0339fc76decb1095f88d3caf56ad1b","tid":801703,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180901/large/1535754000_1468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180901%2Flarge%2F1535754000_1468.jpg&h=729460c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名華裔癌症研究員承認盜取葛蘭素史克公司(GlaxoSmithKline)的商業機密，控方指她打算利用資料在中國成立公司並生產藥物推出市場。<br />\n<br />\n控方指48歲的美籍華裔科學家薛羽(Yu Xue，音譯)是全球頂尖生物化學家，在葛蘭素史克位於費城的研究中心工作約10年。她被控下載一種癌症藥物的研究資料，並以電郵寄到自己的私人賬戶再轉發他人。<br />\n<br />\n控方指同案另有4人，其中兩人在中國，另一人是葛蘭素史克另一位華裔研究員李濤(Tao Li，音譯)。<br />\n<br />\n薛羽與控方達成認罪協議，控方撤消20多條控罪，只控告她一項串謀罪。薛羽周五在庭上說，她不知道該批包括其部份專利申請的研究資料會被視為商業機密。她說：「對我而言，商業機密是公眾不能獲得的資料，而我寄給他人的資料，早已公開。」薛羽指出，她寄出的資料，是其研究專利的初步申請。<br />\n<br />\n法官指控方不需證明她明白那是商業機密，只需證明她知道正與其他人分享機密資料。法官將於12月18日判刑，薛羽最高可被判入獄10年和罰款25萬美元(195萬港元)。她亦可能被追討該批商業機密的價值，最高達20億美元(156億港元)。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"96abf87d83dfdbb49cb78f04ff89ae4f7f3709ed","tid":801703,"uid":8410,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:25:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">美籍華裔科學家薛羽(Yu Xue，音譯)是全球頂尖生物化學家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n可惜佢係電腦白痴"},{"pid":"46be03cf90383cc3e5729f3e65d3e65a19034e38","tid":801703,"uid":74442,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:28:07.000Z","msg":"請大陸閪，自作孽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddaad6649f1226c3666dc4014d7c8ad467b0ce43","tid":801703,"uid":44486,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:28:31.000Z","msg":"個名係xyz 開頭都無個好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c573e50fbac5262207866ece67abe33f3efe8f6","tid":801703,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684fac73da94347c7ddaf1a19bfa9ea337d292ef","tid":801703,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:37:17.000Z","msg":"XYZ"},{"pid":"6b486813e004ac8b8f03adf7f14ebc42a4cc7a8a","tid":801703,"uid":180156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:43:41.000Z","msg":"比大陸人係美國做科學家就預左比人偷喇"},{"pid":"96ca2ac4941d98fb5cd5e21f1543c0696e86c36a","tid":801703,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:46:26.000Z","msg":"傻仔先會請大陸西"},{"pid":"155f647a5e8d3359a7014debc6ef804e52fc63b8","tid":801703,"uid":139251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:34:05.000Z","msg":"請大陸人就預左 integrity？ private property right？食得㗎？"},{"pid":"10c34ac3b8b92fc92265905e4cbbf32ae54b4c5f","tid":801703,"uid":33674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ddaad6649f1226c3666dc4014d7c8ad467b0ce43","tid":801703,"uid":44486,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:28:31.000Z","msg":"個名係xyz 開頭都無個好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實X,Z係真，但係Y好易殺錯良民<br />\ne.g. 邱，遠，余"},{"pid":"f1afa967e05207a500de7fe56597100ebf1461af","tid":801703,"uid":33674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個名係xyz 開頭都無個好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實X,Z係真，但係Y好易殺錯良民<br />\ne.g. 邱，袁，余</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c3676e0bd02566897614698581f0ab987a602cde","tid":801703,"uid":155732,"lik